snippet.title: Robokill: Titan Prime (2008) Full playthrough, Episode 4
snippet.description:
Timestamps
episode 4
 mission 11 00:06
  death #7 25:01
   XP level 34. Failed to outrun a small group of red kamikaze drones while being shot at by a red heavy turret. Toll $1,700
  death #8 30:10
   XP level 35. Crashed into a yellow drone in a cramped space. Toll $1,750
  death #9 30:56
   XP level 35. Attempt #2 of previous death. Crashed into red laser bot. Toll $1,750

 mission 12 54:36
  death #10 58:09
   XP level 37. Eliminated by a small swarm of ultimate bugs. Toll: $1,850
  Boss fight 1:31:45

 mission 13 1:32:34
  death #11 1:34:33
   XP level 40. Swarmed by a trap of ultimate drones. Toll: $2,000
 death #12 2:00:39
   XP level 43. Crashed against a yellow heavy drone while cornered by other enemies. Toll: $2,000
 death #13 2:09:13
   XP level 43. Right mouse click locked the movement towards a fixed direction, leading to a fall thourgh the edge in an easily winnable fight (software bug). Toll: $2,150

Final Boss 2:11:48
Victory 2:13:58
